  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389160/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1773994759\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389160/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1773994759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/389160/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1773994759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Shadow Ninja: Apocalypse is a fast and unforgiving 2D action game where everything depends on your reaction and sense of rhythm.<br><br>You are a ninja in a ruined world. Traps, enemies and constant pressure surround you. Mistakes are not forgiven. Each run is an attempt to go further than before.<br><br>There are no complex systems here. Only movement, combat and survival.<br><br>What’s inside<br><br>- Fast gameplay  <br>The pace never lets you relax. You must stay focused at all times.<br><br>- Simple controls  <br>Easy to start, hard to maintain consistent results.<br><br>- Traps and enemies  <br>Jumps, dodges and attacks flow into one continuous sequence.<br><br>- Short sessions  <br>You can play for a few minutes, but it’s hard to stop.<br><br>- “One more try” effect  <br>Every run makes you want to replay it better.<br><br>The core of the game<br><br>You don’t explore the world.  <br>You try to survive in it.<br><br>And with each attempt, you become faster.",
  "about_the_game": "Shadow Ninja: Apocalypse is a fast and unforgiving 2D action game where everything depends on your reaction and sense of rhythm.<br />\n<br />\nYou are a ninja in a ruined world. Traps, enemies and constant pressure surround you. Mistakes are not forgiven. Each run is an attempt to go further than before.<br />\n<br />\nThere are no complex systems here. Only movement, combat and survival.<br />\n<br />\nWhat’s inside<br />\n<br />\n- Fast gameplay  <br />\nThe pace never lets you relax. You must stay focused at all times.<br />\n<br />\n- Simple controls  <br />\nEasy to start, hard to maintain consistent results.<br />\n<br />\n- Traps and enemies  <br />\nJumps, dodges and attacks flow into one continuous sequence.<br />\n<br />\n- Short sessions  <br />\nYou can play for a few minutes, but it’s hard to stop.<br />\n<br />\n- “One more try” effect  <br />\nEvery run makes you want to replay it better.<br />\n<br />\nThe core of the game<br />\n<br />\nYou don’t explore the world.  <br />\nYou try to survive in it.<br />\n<br />\nAnd with each attempt, you become faster.",
